It is certainly an interesting thing as a DIY project, and would be especially cool as an open source HW/SW project, but I should note that these days there is a ton of cheap Chinese portable consoles (Dingoo, Gemei, Caanoo, Ritmix, and countless others) with emulators, some of them also has TV out. I also recall something similar that had no screen, just a small box with USB and TV out. So if someone just wants a ready-made product, there are existing devices already.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4205">Shiru</a> — Tue Mar 20, 2012 4:56 am</p><hr />
